The scheduler doesn't seem to take account of the dependencies between stages. I have two options "stages can only be scheduled in different sprints", or "multiple stages can be scheduled into one sprint.", when actually the relationships vary. I.e. given an epic has design, build, test stages, I can start to build immediately after design, but can't really test until it's at least part built.

