I'd like to be able to make bulk changes in Portfolio, such as "Move to epic" and "Mark open child items as complete".

Similarly, when importing existing issues, I'd like to be able to assign those issues to parent epics and releases in bulk, rather than by choosing each one individually from a pull down menu.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Portfolio Cloud*. Using *JIRA Portfolio Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JPOSERVER-1857].
  {panel}

As a portfolio user, I want to specify a default estimate for the "Bug" issue type in Unestimated item scheduling.

The bugs in Portfolio are using the default for the Story issue type, which skews the plan because most are not that large.  This is most important when we find defects for stories in the current sprint, which Portfolio gives the default story size and shows the sprint as much larger than it really is.

